---
// BTL Corner section - El Rincón del BTL y Productoras
---

<section class="btl-corner relative py-32 md:py-48 overflow-hidden" id="btl">
	<!-- Background gradient -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-primary via-surface-secondary to-surface-primary"></div>
	<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-purple/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
	<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-cyan/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

	<!-- Content -->
	<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
		<!-- Title -->
		<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black font-display leading-tight mb-8 text-text-primary text-center">
			¿Produces eventos o diseñas
			<br />
			<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan via-brand-accent to-brand-purple bg-clip-text text-transparent">licitaciones?</span>
		</h2>

		<!-- Subtitle -->
		<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed font-light mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
			Conocemos la presión del en vivo. Te entregamos tecnología robusta en formato "marca blanca" para que la integres sin fricción en las propuestas de tus clientes.
		</p>

		<!-- Value Checklist -->
		<div class="space-y-4 mb-12">
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/30 text-text-primary font-medium">
				<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
					<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
				</svg>
				<span>Márgenes claros para tu rentabilidad</span>
			</div>
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-purple/10 border border-brand-purple/30 text-text-primary font-medium">
				<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
					<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
				</svg>
				<span>Hardware industrial calibrado</span>
			</div>
			<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-brand-pink/10 border border-brand-pink/30 text-text-primary font-medium">
				<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-pink flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
					<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
				</svg>
				<span>Soporte presencial para garantizar tranquilidad</span>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- CTA Button -->
		<a href="#contacto" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-brand-cyan text-brand-dark rounded-xl font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-glow-sm hover:scale-105">
			<span>Descargar Fichas Técnicas</span>
			<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
			</svg>
		</a>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.btl-corner {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0e27 0%, #1a1f3a 100%);
	}

	@keyframes slideUp {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.btl-corner h2 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>